
Wiring of Arduino Leonardo and BLEmini:
---------------------------------------

Install Biscuit-FW for BLEmini:
-------------------------------
See http://http://redbearlab.com/blemini/
and https://github.com/RedBearLab/Biscuit.git.
Using version bb24ba63.

Download sketch ./Arduino/blemini_read_digital on Arduino Leonardo:
-------------------------------------------------------------------
Using Arduino 1.0.5.

Install BlueZ 5.12:
-------------------
sudo apt-get install libdbus-1-dev libglib2.0-dev automake libudev-dev libical-dev libreadline-dev
wget https://www.kernel.org/pub/linux/bluetooth/bluez-5.12.tar.gz
tar xvf bluez-5.12.tar.gz
cd bluez-5.12
./configure --disable-systemd
make
sudo make install
sudo cp attrib/gatttool /usr/local/bin/gatttool512

Install pexpect 3.0 :
---------------------
sudo apt-get install python-dev
git clone https://github.com/pexpect/pexpect.git
cd pexpect
git checkout 3.0
sudo python setup.py install

